The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Cop arrest
                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                      Cop arrest
                            
	Ballia, May 15 (PTI): A policeman was arrested today in connection with the racket relating to the smuggling of CRPF and police bullets to the Maoists.        
	Accused Ram Krishna Shukla is a constable armourer at the police lines.         
	On Thursday night, four other policemen were arrested.         
	The racket was busted on April 30 with the arrest of five security personnel and a retired CRPF sub-inspector.                                                                                                                                                           
